{\b0 \cf37 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf37 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Actions taken by port authority in selling certain submerged sovereignty lands and granting permission to purchaser to fill such submerged lands were required to be reviewed by certiorari and complaint for declaratory judgment filed by property owners for determination of legality of actions of authority was unauthorized. 31 F.S.A. Florida Appellate Rules, rules 4.1, 4.5, 
}
{\b1 \cf38 \f2 \i0 \fs20 \chcbpat44 
{\b1 \cf38 \f2 \i0 \fs20 \chcbpat44 
{\b1 \cf38 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
subd
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf37 \f2 \i0 \fs20 \chcbpat2 
}
{\b0 \cf37 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
. c(1).
\par 
}
}
}
