{\b0 \cf37 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \ql \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf37 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf37 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf37 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf37 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
Purchaser of submerged land was necessary party to action for declaratory judgment filed by property owners for determination of legality of actions taken by port authority in selling certain submerged sovereignty lands and granting permission to purchaser to fill such submerged lands. Sp.Acts 1945, c. 23338.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf37 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li30 
